INVINCIBLE IS BACK, and with it, comes bonkers fight scenes, obscenities, gore, and more as we return right where Season 1 left us. Join us as we dissect the latest adventures of Mark Grayson, aka Invincible, as he navigates the challenges of being a superhero while facing off against some of the craziest villains in the galaxy. From shocking plot twists to intense battles, we analyze the evolution of characters like Omni-Man, Mark, Debby, and Cecil, and delve into the moral dilemmas they face. Explore the deeper themes of family, identity, and duty as we unravel the mysteries of this gripping animated series. Don't miss out on our in-depth discussion of Invincible Season 2!

Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

